o	Maintain per-country rate card & markup.
3.	Conversation Window Tracker
o	Calculate 24h customer service window resets; 72h CTWA free window validity; decide â€œfree vs paidâ€ sending path. [linkmobility.com]
4.	AI Assist (LLM + Retrieval)
o	FAQ deflection; intent classification; lead qualification (form fill, NPS, KYC nudges).
o	Safe responses; profanity & PII redaction.
